Package: ggshape
Title: Arrange 'ggplot' facets in arbitrary shapes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jonathan", "Carroll", email = "rpkg@jcarroll.com.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Remove the gridwise constraints of 'facet_wrap' and place plots in arbitrary positions. Example shapes included.
